						<summary>

						<p>Chōḻa, Kulōttuṅga III, 20th year = A.D. 1198.</p>						

						<p>Gift of a piece of <hi rend="italic">dēvadāna</hi> land for a lamp by a native of Kaṉṉi-kuḷattūr in Pulivala-nāḍu in Kāliyūr-kōṭṭam in Jayaṅgoṇḍachōḻa-maṇḍalam. It is said the donor reclaimed the land which had been damaged in floods.</p>						

